source.title: China's Shocking New AI Robot Able To Harm Humans
source.description:
A humanoid AI robot is now walking public streets in China, moving with confidence, precision, and real physical capability. This is not a demo or a lab test. Itâ€™s real-world deployment in everyday environments, and the footage feels unsettling because of how normal it looks. In this video, we break down the viral clips, explain where the robot comes from, why its physical abilities were shown publicly, and what this moment signals about how humanoid AI is quietly entering human spaces.
